-You should have called. Bobby.
-Sorry. Miss Sheen.

82
00:05:03.638 --> 00:05:04.906
We scheduled?

83
00:05:05.139 --> 00:05:06.373
Well. given what happened
to Braxton.

84
00:05:06.507 --> 00:05:07.875
