Why didn't you let him know what
he was getting himself into?

91
00:05:25.793 --> 00:05:27.327
Nobody knew what
he was getting into.

92
00:05:27.460 --> 00:05:28.596
-Hm.
-Anyway. what's it got

93
00:05:28.763 --> 00:05:31.098
