to recover your money.

100
00:05:48.115 --> 00:05:50.585
-You think you can recover it?
-You know I can.

101
00:05:50.818 --> 00:05:52.653
Ooh. but I know
you're too expensive.

102
00:05:52.787 --> 00:05:55.723
Wouldn't Spencer Goldstein
rather see its money back

103
