and getting the same result.

110
00:06:11.672 --> 00:06:13.875
-On what terms?
-Standard sub-contract.

111
00:06:14.008 --> 00:06:16.577
You get deniability. Spencer
Goldstein's hands stay clean.

112
00:06:16.711 --> 00:06:19.814
