to lose a hundred.

118
00:06:33.661 --> 00:06:34.829
You're a fucking nuisance.

119
00:06:36.429 --> 00:06:37.765
Of course
I'm a fucking nuisance.

120
00:06:38.833 --> 00:06:42.270
